    <script type="text/javascript" src="{% static 'admin/js/jquery.init.js' %}"></script>
{% endblock %}
```

Ps: Adding only the `jquery.init.js` file generate the error `Uncaught RangeError: Maximum call stack size exceeded`. So I added `jquery.js` on top and all works. These files comes from [Django code base](https://github.com/django/django/blob/3c447b108ac70757001171f7a4791f493880bf5b/django/contrib/admin/static/admin/js/jquery.init.js).

