@jpmckinney you can't just change it back because once it has been output, you have lost (thrown away) part of the information required to make the necessary decisions - any subsequent program in the pipeline only sees the output of the most recent program, it has no access to the original input.  like any other tool, csvformat can only work with what it has, not what was discarded.

